🔥 Saengjonsul Collection – Exclusive Badge NFTs 🔥

Step into the world of Saengjonsul, a korean martial art of Self-Defense that embodies strategy, power, and precision. This exclusive NFT collection features 30 unique badges, each minted in only 13 numbered editions, ensuring rarity and prestige.

🔹 30 unique designs inspired by iconic Saengjonsul training locations worldwide.

🔹 Ultra-limited series: Only 13 editions of each badge will ever exist.
🔹 The last 3 editions of every badge will be held for future high-value releases.

💎 A fusion of martial arts heritage, digital collectibles, and pure exclusivity.
📦 Worldwide shipping included with every purchase.

🚀 Secure your Saengjonsul NFT before it’s gone forever!

🌌 Cosmic Gems – A Celestial NFT Collection 💎✨

From the fiery Inferno Ruby to the ethereal Ethereal Diamond, each Cosmic Gem tells a story of interstellar creation and cosmic balance.

Holders gain:
🔹 Exclusive ownership of a rare, one-of-a-kind collectible.
🔹 A place in a cosmic journey that blends art, mythology, and celestial energy.
🔹 A chance to own a digital fragment of the universe itself.

🚀 Claim your Cosmic Gem and become part of the stars.

collections.name: FurryBank
collections.description:
"Where Wealth Meets the Wild"

FurryBank is a one-of-a-kind NFT collection that merges the untamed beauty of wildlife with the timeless value of currency. Each digital banknote features intricately designed animal-inspired artwork, blending financial elegance with the power of nature.

From roaring lions to wise owls, every piece in this collection embodies a unique fusion of strength, intelligence, and economic symbolism. With a sleek and luxurious aesthetic, FurryBank represents more than just digital art—it’s a statement of value, trust, and exclusivity in the Web3 era.

Own a piece of the wild economy. Welcome to FurryBank. 🏦🐾💰
